
# Quiz Website

This is a simple quiz website project that allows users to take quizzes on various topics.
 It's designed to be user-friendly and easy to customize.
  Whether you want to use it for educational purposes, as a fun quiz platform,
   or for any other application, this project provides a solid foundation to build upon.

