## Installation

1. Clone the repository:

    ```
    git clone https://github.com/yourusername/quiz-website.git
    ```

2. Change to the project directory:

    ```
    cd quiz-website
    ```

3. Install dependencies:

    ```
    npm install
    ```

4. Set up your database and configure the database connection.

5. Start the server:

    ```
    npm start
    ```

6. Access the website at `http://localhost:3000` in your web browser.

## Usage

1. Register as a user or log in if you already have an account.
2. Browse available quizzes by category.
3. Select a quiz to take.
4. Answer the questions to the best of your ability.
5. See your score at the end of the quiz.
6. Check the leaderboards to compare your performance with others.

